g and the ongoing reality of Christ's enfleshed existence — the incarnation is not a past event only but an abiding truth (1 John 4:2-3)."},{"num":8,"words":[{"h":"βλέπετε","t":"blépō","s":"G991","g":"behold","m":"verb 2nd present active imperative plural","l":"βλέπω"},{"h":"ἑαυτούς","t":"heautoû","s":"G1438","g":"alone","m":"personal pronoun accusative plural masculine","l":"ἑαυτοῦ"},{"h":"ἵνα","t":"hína","s":"G2443","g":"albeit","m":"conjunction"},{"h":"μὴ","t":"mḗ","s":"G3361","g":"any but","m":"adverb","l":"μή"},{"h":"⸀ἀπολέσητε","t":"apóllymi","s":"G622","g":"destroy","m":"verb 2nd aorist active subjunctive plural","l":"ἀπόλλυμι"},{"h":"ἃ","t":"hós","s":"G3739","g":"one","m":"relative pronoun accusative plural neuter","l":"ὅς"},{"h":"⸀εἰργασάμεθα","t":"ergázomai","s":"G2038","g":"commit","m":"verb 1st aorist middle indicative plural","l":"ἐργάζομαι"},{"h":"ἀλλὰ","t":"allá","s":"G235","g":"and","m":"conjunction","l":"ἀλλά"},{"h":"μισθὸν","t":"misthós","s":"G3408","g":"hire","m":"noun accusative singular masculine","l":"μισθός"},{"h":"πλήρη","t":"plḗrēs","s":"G4134","g":"full","m":"adjective accusative singular masculine","l":"πλήρης"},{"h":"⸀ἀπολάβητε","t":"apolambánō","s":"G618","g":"receive","m":"verb 2nd aorist active subjunctive plural","l":"ἀπολαμβάνω"}],"flow":"Watch yourselves, that you do not lose what we have worked for, but that you may receive a full reward."},{"num":9,"words":[{"h":"πᾶς","t":"pâs","s":"G3956","g":"all (manner of","m":"adjective nominative singular masculine"},{"h":"ὁ","t":"ho","s":"G3588","g":"the","m":"article nominative singular masculine"},{"h":"⸀προάγων","t":"proágō","s":"G4254","g":"bring (forth","m":"verb present active participle nominative singular masculine","l":"προάγω"},{"h":"καὶ","t":"kaí","s":"G2532","g":"and","m":"conjunction","l":"καί"},{"h":"μὴ","t":"mḗ","s":"G3361","g":"any but","m":"adverb","l":"μή"},{"h":"μένων","t":"ménō","s":"G3306","g":"abide","m":"verb present active participle nominative singular masculine","l